The git version of our paper on broken lines and greedy bases

To write a marginal note add an alias to the \say command similar to the ones
already there and write your comments with
\saySS{This comment was written by Salvatore}

To get write access to this repository get a github account and e-mail your
username to me: I will add you shortly after.


